title: Statement by White House Press Secretary Jen Psaki on the Bilateral Virtual Meeting Between President Joe Biden and President Andrés Manuel López Obrador | The White House
content: On Monday, March 1, President Joe Biden will meet with President Andrés Manuel López Obrador. In this virtual event, the two leaders will discuss cooperation on migration, joint development efforts in Southern Mexico and Central America, COVID-19 recovery, and economic cooperation.###
